{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>IMPORTANT:\u00a0We are aware of the optimization issues and are working on a launcher that will allow the game to run smoothly even on older setups.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Thank you for your patience.</u><br><br>Warning:</strong> The game is made by two friends alongside their regular jobs. Please note that it may contain bugs. We would appreciate it if you report any bugs you find on our Discord, and we will try to fix them as soon as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">In the game PeakPals, your goal is to reach the top and board the airship that will take you away. Along the way, there are various obstacles and puzzles. You can choose from different modes, ranging from the easiest, where you can save your progress, to the hardest, where a single mistake will result in a tough fall back down.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the game, you can also find wood, which allows you to build wooden platforms to overcome more difficult sections or passages that you struggle to pass. However, these platforms do not save after you exit the game, so you must use them wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is designed for up to 6 players. <br>Each player has a weapon, but you have to find the ammo on your way up. You will also find grenades along the way. You can use these weapons to knock other players down or even help a friend with a well-placed grenade under their feet to propel them to a higher platform. So, whether you decide to help each other or cause trouble is entirely up to you. Do you think you can make it to the top? <br><br>Please note that this is early access, and some bugs might still be present, but I believe most have been fixed. If you encounter any issues, please report them to: <a href=\"mailto:support@kyrsoftstudio.com\">support@kyrsoftstudio.com</a> or on my Discord.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Reach 300m - HARD MOD",